[7] Hong Kong Recall
Date: Wed 1 Apr 2009
Source: XinHuaNet [edited]
<http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2009-04/01/content_11115535.htm>


The Center for Food Safety (CFS) of Hong Kong advised people Wed 1
Apr 2009 not to consume certain batches of USA pistachio products
which are suspected to have been contaminated with _Salmonella_.

A total of 28 "Planters" products and 8 "Back to Nature" products are affected.

